Upstream project: https://github.com/ARC-MX/sgcc_electricity_new
Derived project: https://github.com/MaribelHearm/sgcc-home-assistant-bridg

Major changes in this derived work include:
- modular refactoring of configuration, redaction, browser, login, session,
  scraper, parser, store, model, Home Assistant mapping and publisher modules;
- Path B scraping from SGCC Vue2/Vuex store and component data;
- SQLite local fact store for account data, fetch runs, session checks and
  publisher state;
- multimodal LLM assisted Tencent click-captcha solving with QR-code fallback;
- per-run headful Chromium/Xvfb browser lifecycle that closes after use;
- Home Assistant MQTT Discovery publishing with REST compatibility.

